d":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:28:29.000Z","msg":"當時香港警察學院教官麥啟立警司充當死因庭專家證人<br />\n<ins>老屈係因為司機反抗而導致意外<br />\n<br />\n</ins>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:36:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>箍着死者頸部，向上提起令死者雙腳離地，頭部轉動近90度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢下反唔反抗都斷氣啦"},{"pid":"7648bc1f8550ea669d178367ec6169db3daaa7de","tid":1804272,"uid":212884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:38:29.000Z","msg":"香港法治已死"},{"pid":"2df4fa9b1b82bc58a57cc9b1fe167cd12ad82119","tid":1804272,"uid":212884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:39:20.000Z","msg":"黑警殺人唔洗你教"},{"pid":"e20a5d21fcb79faacd4f403e3963045d7a704346","tid":1804272,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:53:34.000Z","msg":"如果條友唔係警犬一早坐左監<br />\n因為係<ins>拉犯過程中殺人</ins><br />\n如果告入左最鐘意打犯的反黑就一定玩野"}]}